<!-- ════════════════ WHO I AM ════════════════ -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-tag tag-purple">📋 Who I Am</div>
    <div class="profile-layout">
      <div class="profile-intro">
        <div class="profile-name">Alec Doran-Twyford</div>
        <div class="profile-tagline">Loveable nerd · Software Engineer · Welwyn Garden City</div>
        <p>Hi, I'm Alec! This little site started as a slide deck I made for myself — a reminder of who I am and what I love. I then realised it could be a fun way to skip some of the small talk and give you a real sense of me from the start.</p>
        <p>So here's the honest (and slightly chaotic) introduction: the facts, the photos, and the bits that make me, me. If you like what you see, my contact details are just a little further down.</p>

        <div class="fact-grid">
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-icon">🚹</span><div><div class="fact-label">Gender</div><div class="fact-value">Male</div></div></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-icon">❤️</span><div><div class="fact-label">Orientation</div><div class="fact-value">Straight</div></div></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-icon">🗣️</span><div><div class="fact-label">Pronouns</div><div class="fact-value">He / Him / They / Them</div></div></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-icon">🎂</span><div><div class="fact-label">Age</div><div class="fact-value">35 · 19 May (Taurus)</div></div></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-icon">💼</span><div><div class="fact-label">Profession</div><div class="fact-value">Software Engineer</div></div></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-icon">🎓</span><div><div class="fact-label">Education</div><div class="fact-value">BSc Computer Science</div></div></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-icon">🌍</span><div><div class="fact-label">Nationality</div><div class="fact-value">British / New Zealander</div></div></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-icon">📍</span><div><div class="fact-label">Living in</div><div class="fact-value">Welwyn Garden City</div></div></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-icon">📏</span><div><div class="fact-label">Height</div><div class="fact-value">~5'8"</div></div></div>
          <div class="fact"><span class="fact-icon">🖤</span><div><div class="fact-label">Favourite Colour</div><div class="fact-value">Black</div></div></div>
          <div class="fact wide"><span class="fact-icon">🌱</span><div><div class="fact-label">Politics</div><div class="fact-value">Liberal Left (Green Party)</div></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="profile-photo">
        <img src="img/coverphoto/index.png" alt="Alec Doran-Twyford" data-zoom>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

