<!-- ════════════════ WHAT I CAN BE ════════════════ -->
<section id="boyfriend-mode">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-tag tag-rose">❤️ What I Can Be</div>
    <h2>What Dating Me Could Look Like</h2>
    <p class="lead">A peek at "boyfriend mode" — the little things I love doing for the person I'm with.</p>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/boyfriend-mode/a couple hugging.png" alt="A couple hugging" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">🤗</span><span class="feature-text">Always supportive and caring — there through the good and bad times, with great hugs, forehead kisses and massages.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/boyfriend-mode/person getting coffee from a shop.png" alt="Getting coffee" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">☕</span><span class="feature-text">Always knowing your coffee order &amp; keeping your favourite snack on hand.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/boyfriend-mode/person taking photo.png" alt="Taking a photo" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">📸</span><span class="feature-text">Your personal photographer — making sure you always look great.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/boyfriend-mode/boyfirend driving his passanger princess.png" alt="Driving" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">👑</span><span class="feature-text">Full passenger-princess treatment whenever we're on the road.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/boyfriend-mode/person recing morning text message.png" alt="A morning text" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">💬</span><span class="feature-text">Good morning &amp; good night texts, every day.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/boyfriend-mode/person suprising someone with flowers.png" alt="Surprise flowers" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">💐</span><span class="feature-text">Random flowers and cute little gifts, just because.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/boyfriend-mode/cartoon of a person sharing tiktok memes.png" alt="Sharing memes" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">🐸</span><span class="feature-text">Pebbling you with hundreds of perfectly curated memes.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/boyfriend-mode/a google calander invite for cute date.png" alt="A calendar invite for a date" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">📅</span><span class="feature-text">Organising cute dates (and yes, adding them to Google Calendar).</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/boyfriend-mode/person writing a google doc about his girl friend.png" alt="Writing a doc" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">📊</span><span class="feature-text">Keeping docs &amp; spreadsheets of the things that matter to you and our plans.</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════════════════ LOOKING FOR ════════════════ -->
<section id="looking-for">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-tag tag-gold">✨ What I'm Looking For</div>
    <h2>An Invitation, Not a Checklist</h2>
    <p class="lead">I have a full, happy life — I'm just hoping to share it. Here's the kind of "us" I'm dreaming about.</p>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/looking-for/couple cooking.png" alt="A couple cooking" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">🍳</span><span class="feature-text">Cooking and baking together on a cosy evening.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/looking-for/couple playing video games.png" alt="A couple gaming" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">🎮</span><span class="feature-text">Co-op games and friendly rivalry on the sofa.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/looking-for/couple going exploring nature.png" alt="A couple exploring nature" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">🌿</span><span class="feature-text">Adventures, travel and finding amazing food places.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/looking-for/couple watching movie togehter.png" alt="A couple watching a movie" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">🍿</span><span class="feature-text">Lazy days at home with a film and good company.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/looking-for/couple enjoying tea on the couch.png" alt="A couple enjoying tea" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">🫖</span><span class="feature-text">Slow mornings, tea, and easy quiet time together.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <img src="img/looking-for/couple at the gym working out.png" alt="A couple at the gym" loading="lazy">
        <div class="feature-body"><span class="feature-icon">💪</span><span class="feature-text">Cheering each other on to be our best selves.</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="value-cols">
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3>Adventures Together</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Someone open to my interests (and excited to share theirs)</li>
          <li>Travelling &amp; going on adventures</li>
          <li>Hunting down amazing food places</li>
          <li>Walks, fun activities, and cosy days in</li>
          <li>Cooking, baking, games, films — together</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <h3>What I Value</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Clear and open communication</li>
          <li>Pushing each other to be our best selves</li>
          <li>Willingness to work through the hard times</li>
          <li>Quality time and mutual affection</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

