      <!-- Politics & Religion -->
      <article class="acc-item">
        <button class="acc-header" aria-expanded="false"><span class="acc-emoji">🏛️</span><span class="acc-title">Politics &amp; Religion <span class="acc-hint">— where I stand</span></span><span class="acc-chevron">▾</span></button>
        <div class="acc-body"><div class="acc-body-inner"><div class="acc-content">
          <p>I'm Liberal Left (Green Party at present). My main thing is supporting the poorest so we can all be more equal. My general philosophy: <strong style="color:var(--text);">"Try not to be a dick!"</strong></p>
          <div class="two-cols">
            <div class="list-block">
              <h3>Policy &amp; Support</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Simpler tax rules &amp; closing loopholes</li>
                <li>Nationalising utilities &amp; transport</li>
                <li>Human rights &amp; LGBTQIA+ (incl. Trans rights)</li>
                <li>Disability &amp; neurodivergent equality</li>
                <li>Race &amp; gender equality, reproductive rights</li>
                <li>The environment</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="list-block">
              <h3>Religion</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Raised Christian; I now choose not to hold a belief system and just try to be as good and kind as I can</li>
                <li>I respect others' beliefs and try to educate myself on them</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="photo-grid" style="margin-top:16px;">
            <img src="img/politics/human right sign.png" alt="Human rights" loading="lazy">
